addTicketTier(uint256,string,uint256,uin.details: Add ticket tier to an event

buyTicket(uint256,uint256,uint256,string.details: Purchase a multi-person ticket for an event

cancelEvent(uint256).details: Cancel an event and process refunds

createEvent(string,string,string,uint256.details: Create a new event (organizer pays listing fee)

getTicketInfo(uint256).details: View function to get complete ticket information

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

verifyAndUseTicket(uint256).details: Verify and use a ticket (for entry)

verifyTicket(uint256).details: View function to check ticket validity without modifying state
